text: Public center of Raquette Lake village Raquette Lake is a hamlet in the town of Long Lake in Hamilton County, New York, United States. The community is on New York State Route 28 on the west side of Raquette Lake. Great Camp Sagamore is in the hamlet.http://www.greatcampsagamore.org/ ==References== == External links == * raquettelake.org Category:Hamlets in New York (state) Category:Hamlets in Hamilton County, New York
